original: Öhrstam, Gunnar Johan Ernst, apotekare, Ödeshög, f. 10/7/92 i Ör, Kro-nob. 1. G. 27 m. Ebba Sofia Nilsson. Barn: Torsten Karl Gunnar f. 27, Erik Ernst Gunnar 29. — Studiex. i Växjö 18, farm. kand. 22, apot :ex. 27. Elev v. apot. Hjorten i Sthlm 19-21, anst. v. apot. i Alingsås o. Arvika, Fläkta Örn i Malimö, Lejonet i Sthllm samt Lejonet i Upps., priv. å apot. i Ödes-höig sed. 43’.
translated: Öhrstam, Gunnar Johan Ernst, pharmacist, Ödeshög, b. 10/7/92 in Ör, Kronoberg county. 1st marriage on 27, to Ebba Sofia Nilsson. Children: Torsten Karl Gunnar b. 27, Erik Ernst Gunnar b. 29. — Graduated from Växjö College in 1918, pharmaceutical candidate in 1922, pharmacist's exam in 1927. Was an intern at Hjorten pharmacy in Stockholm from 1919 to 1921, employed at pharmacies in Alingsås and Arvika, Fläkta Örn in Malmö, Lejonet in Stockholm, and Lejonet in Uppsala. Settled privately at the Ödeshög pharmacy since 1943.
